{"tid":907853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件柒事","createTime":"2018-11-19T06:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T07:12:21.000Z","uid":222785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e67bb922f8dd87a7d1ec3c5e3ce9c709e13f65a","tid":907853,"uid":222785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:48:05.000Z","msg":"前面班領袖宣誓嗰陣時本身我瞓緊覺嘅<br />\n突然間畀隔離嗰個同學拍醒咗搞到我即刻彈咗起身一齊宣誓<br />\n柒到喊"},{"pid":"a375a03848e9ac5f95e1df3c317fcc189f9a2a18","tid":907853,"uid":93649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:57:08.000Z","msg":"吾知你做乜春<br />\n我就柒過你<br />\n有次歌唱頒獎典禮沖左出去拎獎<br />\n點知唔係我"},{"pid":"fb9b7e79d7395ed4dbe4da71857e282b4f0a3fdc","tid":907853,"uid":214363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:58:47.000Z","msg":"都係姓關呀嘛"},{"pid":"44b23af74ca93a94ff5a0e2006dea6f040921f3b","tid":907853,"uid":187076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"叫錯老師做阿媽"},{"pid":"b976e6a896ae82f8f7e117dee805b6f480d81c46","tid":907853,"uid":222785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a375a03848e9ac5f95e1df3c317fcc189f9a2a18","tid":907853,"uid":93649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:57:08.000Z","msg":"吾知你做乜春<br />\n我就柒過你<br />\n有次歌唱頒獎典禮沖左出去拎獎<br />\n點知唔係我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:12:21.000Z","msg":"我間學校呢就係隔一個星期一次週會嘅<br />\n週會多數就係聽講座<br />\n然後有一次我唔記得咗係週會以為正常上堂<br />\n就匿埋咗喺禮堂後面瞓覺<br />\n然後當週會開始點人數嗰陣時發現少咗我<br />\n我就好柒咁畀班主任喺禮堂後面捉咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係全校面前 屌"}]}